com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability, com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.DeployModelObject, com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.internal.core.InternalDeployModelObject, User, WindowsLocalUser, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject
public class WindowsLocalUserImpl
extends UserImpl
implements WindowsLocalUser

An implementation of the model object 'Windows Local User'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Account Description
  • Account Disabled
  • Account Locked
  • Change Password Next Logon
  • Enable Remote Control
  • Full Name
  • Home Folder
  • Logon Script
  • Password Never Expires
  • Profile Path
  • User Account Type
  • User Cannot Change Password
  • User Sid
  • User Sid Type
